snippet.title: Seed: Pre-Alpha Teaser - The Formation
snippet.description:
The roots are growing. The correlations are forming. This is only the beginning. Watch the formation in the latest teaser of Seed. Join the Discord: http://bit.ly/Seed_Discord
Sign up to Seed here: http://bit.ly/join_seed

Seed is a boundless journey for human survival, fueled by discovery, collaboration, and genuine emotion. An MMO Simulation by Klang. Powered by SpatialOS.

Music by Sveinbjörn Thorarensen.

All in-game footage is work in progress. 

“Watch the Formation.”

– Follow the Seed Community --

Discord: http://bit.ly/Seed_Discord
Reddit: http://bit.ly/Seed_Reddit
Facebook: http://bit.ly/seed_facebook
Twitter: http://bit.ly/seed_twitter
Instagram: http://bit.ly/seed_instagram

Website: https://www.seed-online.com/
